 Finance+ | Creative Solutions Web Ecosystem
   #​A high-performance, 5-page web application architecture designed for modern fintech and creative agencies. This project translates a dark-mode, high-contrast UI into a fully responsive HTML5 and CSS3 codebase.
   ​## Project Overview
      ​Finance+ is a conceptual finance management and portfolio platform. It utilizes a "Lime & Charcoal" design system, prioritizing visual hierarchy and clear data presentation. The project features a unified global navigation and footer across all modules to ensure a seamless user experience.
    ​### Key Features
   ​5-Page Architecture: Home, Wallet (Dashboard), Analytics (Data), Portfolio (Work), and Contact.
   ​Immersive Background System: Fixed-position abstract background with a 75% dark overlay for maximum text legibility.
   ​Responsive Grid Layouts: Optimized using CSS Flexbox and Grid for both desktop and mobile viewing.
 ​Consistent Branding: Centralized CSS variable system for neon accent colors and dark-mode themes.
 `# Setup Instructions
​Clone/Download the project files to your local machine.
​Asset Management: Place your background image in the root folder or update the url() in style.css under the .bg-image-container class.
​Deployment: Open index.html in any modern web browser or host via GitHub Pages/Vercel.
